IF YOU THINK ABOUT MY THREE
DECADES AT WELLINGTON, IT WAS

00:03:23.000 --> 00:03:26.999
EXPANDING IN EQUITIES THAT
FIRST DECADE, EXPANDING IN

00:03:27.000 --> 00:03:32.999
FIXED INCOME IN THE DECADE OF
