00:04:07.000 --> 00:04:09.999
WHAT IS THE DIFFERENCE BETWEEN
RUNNING A LONG-ONLY FUND AND A

00:04:10.000 --> 00:04:11.999
HEDGE FUND?
A HEDGE FUND YOU CAN SHORT BUT

00:04:12.000 --> 00:04:16.999
YOU CAN ALSO CHARGE A CARRIED
INTEREST RATE. JEAN:

00:04:17.000 --> 00:04:18.999
WHEN WE GO TO CLIENTS, OUR
