00:04:24.000 --> 00:04:28.999
HAVE.
BACK TO THE OPPORTUNITY SET, AS

00:04:29.000 --> 00:04:32.999
A GLOBAL INDUSTRY ANALYST, I
WAS RESPONSIBLE FOR THE

00:04:33.000 --> 00:04:35.999
OPPORTUNITY SET, WHICH MEANT I
HAD LONG POSITIONS AND I CAN

00:04:36.000 --> 00:04:40.999
RECOMMEND PEOPLE AVOID THINGS.
