00:04:41.000 --> 00:04:41.999
BENCHMARK AGAINST WHICH YOU ARE
MEASURING ARE HARDER TO GET

00:04:42.000 --> 00:04:44.999
CLIENTS?
IN OTHER WORDS, THERE IS SO

