00:05:49.000 --> 00:05:51.999
THAT IS WHY WE HAVE BEEN
SUCCESSFUL OVER TIME AND GROWN

00:05:52.000 --> 00:05:53.999
OVER TIME. DAVID:
WHAT KIND OF RATE OF RETURN DO

