00:37:18.951 --> 00:37:19.950
ENDURANCE DRIVER, IT'S ALL
ABOUT COMPROMISE.

00:37:19.951 --> 00:37:22.950
IT IS ABOUT GETTING YOUR
TEAMMATES TO YOUR LEVEL, OR

00:37:22.951 --> 00:37:25.950
EVEN HIGHER THAN WHERE YOU ARE,
BECAUSE THEN YOU KNOW EVEN IF

00:37:25.951 --> 00:37:26.950
YOU ARE THE SLOWEST GUY IN THE
CAR, YOU KNOW YOU ARE QUICK.

00:37:26.951 --> 00:37:28.950
MATT:
YOU MUST WORK ON MAXIMIZING

00:37:28.951 --> 00:37:31.950
