00:37:40.951 --> 00:37:43.950
NIGHT, DRIVING WHILE TIRED?
WHAT IS IT LIKE SEEING THE SUN

00:37:43.951 --> 00:37:46.950
RISE AS YOU ARE DOING 185 MILES
AN HOUR DOWN A STRAIGHT? JENSON:

00:37:46.951 --> 00:37:49.950
AT LE MANS YOU ARE ALWAYS
JETLAGGED, BASICALLY.

00:37:49.951 --> 00:37:53.950
YOU KNOW, THAT IS THE FEELING
THAT YOU HAVE WHEN YOU ARE

00:37:53.951 --> 00:37:57.950
DRIVING THE CAR.
YOU ARE JETLAGGED.

00:37:57.951 --> 00:37:59.950
