SUNSET IS GREAT.

00:38:51.951 --> 00:38:53.950
SUNRISE, THE BEST MOMENT OF THE
RACE. YOU KNOW, IT REALLY IS.

00:38:53.951 --> 00:38:55.950
WHEN THE SUN RISES AND YOU SEE
HOW DIRTY THE CARS ARE.

00:38:55.951 --> 00:38:58.950
YOU HAVE COME THROUGH THE NIGHT.
YOU KIND OF FEEL LIKE YOU ARE

00:38:58.951 --> 00:39:01.950
AT THE END ALREADY, EVEN THOUGH
YOU HAVE ANOTHER 10 HOURS TO GO.

00:39:01.951 --> 00:39:04.950
SO, THAT MOMENT IS A VERY
SPECIAL MOMENT, KNOWING YOU

00:39:04.951 --> 00:39:07.950
HAVE GOT THROUGH THE NIGHT, YOU
HAVE NOT HAD ISSUES, YOU ARE

00:39:07.951 --> 00:39:09.950
STILL IN IT WITH A CHANCE OF A
WIN. MICHELLE:

00:39:09.951 --> 00:39:10.950
THE IRON DAMES WAS FORMED IN
2018.

