00:40:28.951 --> 00:40:31.950
PROVING TO YOUR GIRLS THAT IT
IS POSSIBLE, BECAUSE WE HAD A

00:40:31.951 --> 00:40:34.950
DREAM WHEN WE WERE THEIR AGE.
BACK THEN, WHEN I WAS VERY

00:40:34.951 --> 00:40:36.950
YOUNG, IT WAS DIFFICULT TO HAVE
SOMEBODY TO LOOK UP TO IN TERMS

00:40:36.951 --> 00:40:38.950
